1
00:00:07,140 --> 00:00:10,677
( Dio screams )

2
00:00:10,777 --> 00:00:11,845
THE HAMON...

3
00:00:11,912 --> 00:00:15,181
HAS ALMOST REACHED
MY HEAD AND BRAIN.

4
00:00:15,281 --> 00:00:16,850
MUST DO SOMETHING.

5
00:00:16,917 --> 00:00:19,753
MOVE, ARM. MOVE!

6
00:00:19,820 --> 00:00:21,021
( gags )

7
00:00:21,087 --> 00:00:22,856
♪

8
00:00:32,599 --> 00:00:36,102
Apothecary: OHH. ( gasping )

9
00:00:36,169 --> 00:00:38,038
LORD DIO.

10
00:00:39,205 --> 00:00:41,608
WE'LL GET A NEW BODY FOR YOU.

11
00:00:48,148 --> 00:00:52,052
Narrator: EXCERPT FROM
THE DECEMBER 4, 1888, EDITION

12
00:00:52,118 --> 00:00:53,954
OF THE "LONDON PRESS:"

13
00:00:54,020 --> 00:00:58,224
"IT HAS BEEN REPORTED
THAT 73 OF THE 452 RESIDENTS

14
00:00:58,291 --> 00:01:00,493
"IN THE TOWN
OF WIND KNIGHTS LOT

15
00:01:00,561 --> 00:01:02,836
"HAVE GONE MISSING OVERNIGHT.

16
00:01:02,903 --> 00:01:05,405
"THE POLICE HAVE BEEN
PURSUING LINES OF INQUIRY

17
00:01:05,506 --> 00:01:08,575
"BASED ON CERTAIN
WITNESS ACCOUNTS.

18
00:01:08,642 --> 00:01:10,911
"THESE ACCOUNTS STATE
THAT FOUR OUTSIDERS

19
00:01:10,977 --> 00:01:13,079
"WERE SEEN BURNING
A MAN'S CLOTHING

20
00:01:13,179 --> 00:01:14,915
"AT THE BASE OF A NEARBY CLIFF.

21
00:01:15,015 --> 00:01:17,718
"ONE OF THE FOUR WAS REPORTEDLY
WIELDING A LARGE HAMMER

22
00:01:17,751 --> 00:01:21,855
AND USING IT TO SMASH
A CURIOUS STONE MASK."

23
00:01:22,889 --> 00:01:25,091
Speedwagon:
OUR WORK HERE IS DONE.

24
00:01:25,158 --> 00:01:27,093
♪

25
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:36,703
( singing in Japanese )

26
00:02:57,624 --> 00:02:59,526
( bells pealing )

27
00:02:59,593 --> 00:03:01,502
Speedwagon:
"HEIR TO THE JOESTAR FORTUNE,

28
00:03:01,535 --> 00:03:04,370
"JONATHAN JOESTAR WEDS ERINA,

29
00:03:04,470 --> 00:03:07,541
"ONLY DAUGHTER
OF THE PENDLETONS.

30
00:03:07,608 --> 00:03:10,844
THE COUPLE WILL TRAVEL
TO THE AMERICAS."

31
00:03:10,877 --> 00:03:12,045
NICE.

32
00:03:12,145 --> 00:03:13,046
( gasps )

33
00:03:13,146 --> 00:03:14,515
BLAZES!

34
00:03:14,548 --> 00:03:17,017
LOOK WHAT TIME IT IS!

35
00:03:17,050 --> 00:03:18,952
THEIR SHIP'S ABOUT TO LEAVE!

36
00:03:19,019 --> 00:03:20,954
♪

37
00:03:23,056 --> 00:03:25,125
OI!

38
00:03:25,191 --> 00:03:27,160
Poco: EH? MR. SPEEDWAGON!

39
00:03:27,227 --> 00:03:29,896
YOU ALMOST MISSED
BEING ABLE TO SAY GOODBYE.

40
00:03:29,996 --> 00:03:31,565
Speedwagon: SORRY I'M SO LATE.

41
00:03:31,632 --> 00:03:33,066
SO THEN, WHERE ARE THEY?

42
00:03:33,166 --> 00:03:35,068
Poco: THEY'RE BOTH
ONBOARD THE SHIP.

43
00:03:35,168 --> 00:03:35,969
Speedwagon: EH?!

44
00:03:36,036 --> 00:03:38,204
Poco: IT'S ABOUT READY TO SAIL.

45
00:03:38,238 --> 00:03:39,573
Speedwagon: WHAT? IT IS?

46
00:03:39,673 --> 00:03:41,642
WHERE ARE THEY?
I'VE GOT TO SEE THEM.

47
00:03:41,708 --> 00:03:43,910
Priest: NOW THEN, FATHER STYX,

48
00:03:43,977 --> 00:03:47,881
WE EXPECT TO HEAR GREAT THINGS
FROM YOUR MISSION TO MEXICO.

49
00:03:48,915 --> 00:03:51,051
Styx: I'LL CERTAINLY
DO WHAT I CAN.

50
00:03:52,218 --> 00:03:54,755
Speedwagon: JONATHAN JOESTAR!
WHERE ARE YOU?!

51
00:03:54,855 --> 00:03:56,322
Longshoreman:
WATCH WHERE YOU'RE GOIN'!

52
00:03:56,389 --> 00:03:59,425
WHAT MAKES THIS THING
SO BLASTED HEAVY, ANYWAY?

53
00:03:59,492 --> 00:04:00,661
Longshoreman #2:
HOW SHOULD I KNOW?

54
00:04:00,727 --> 00:04:02,268
WE BEEN HIRED
BY THAT ASIAN BLOKE,

55
00:04:02,335 --> 00:04:03,604
SO WE MOVE IT WHERE HE SAYS.

56
00:04:03,670 --> 00:04:05,606
‐ ( thumping )
‐ Longshoreman #1: HMM?

57
00:04:05,672 --> 00:04:07,373
‐ ( deep breath )
‐ Longshoreman #1: HMM?

58
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:08,274
( gasps )

59
00:04:09,876 --> 00:04:13,079
OI. DID‐‐DID YOU BOYS
HEAR THAT?

60
00:04:13,113 --> 00:04:15,415
Longshoreman #2: QUIT FLAPPIN'
YOUR BLASTED CAKE HOLE.

61
00:04:15,448 --> 00:04:16,850
‐ ( bell ringing )
‐ NOW MOVE IT!

62
00:04:16,917 --> 00:04:19,119
WE DON'T GET PAID
'TIL THIS JOB'S DONE.

63
00:04:19,219 --> 00:04:20,754
( ringing continue )

64
00:04:22,022 --> 00:04:24,090
Speedwagon: OW. RUDDY HOOLIGANS.

65
00:04:24,124 --> 00:04:25,792
‐ Poco: MR. SPEEDWAGON.
‐ Speedwagon: HMM?

66
00:04:25,859 --> 00:04:27,961
Poco: LOOK. THEY'RE UP THERE.

67
00:04:28,061 --> 00:04:29,462
HELLO!

68
00:04:29,530 --> 00:04:31,297
JONATHAN!

69
00:04:31,364 --> 00:04:33,066
♪

70
00:04:33,133 --> 00:04:35,201
Speedwagon:
WHAT A BEAUTIFUL SIGHT.

71
00:04:35,268 --> 00:04:38,471
I WISH YOU
A LONG, LOVE‐FILLED LIFE.

72
00:04:38,538 --> 00:04:40,406
I'LL ALWAYS BE HERE FOR YOU.

73
00:04:40,473 --> 00:04:44,077
IF YOU EVER NEED ME,
JUST CALL. I'LL BE THERE.

74
00:04:45,311 --> 00:04:46,647
THOUGH AT THE MOMENT,

75
00:04:46,747 --> 00:04:49,550
I'D JUST BE IN THE WAY, EH?

76
00:04:49,616 --> 00:04:51,718
( ship's horn blows )

77
00:04:53,620 --> 00:04:55,488
‐ Crowd: BYE!
‐ ( Poco laughs )

78
00:04:55,589 --> 00:04:59,259
‐ Crowd: BYE!
‐ Poco: BON VOYAGE!

79
00:04:59,325 --> 00:05:02,603
HAVE A WONDERFUL TRIP!

80
00:05:02,669 --> 00:05:04,971
♪

81
00:05:17,317 --> 00:05:19,252
♪

82
00:05:26,192 --> 00:05:27,127
( Erina gasps )

83
00:05:29,596 --> 00:05:30,931
( bird chirps )

84
00:05:30,997 --> 00:05:33,466
POOR LITTLE BIRD, ALL ALONE.

85
00:05:33,534 --> 00:05:34,835
DID YOU LOSE YOUR FLOCK?

86
00:05:34,868 --> 00:05:36,036
( wings flap )

87
00:05:42,709 --> 00:05:44,545
JoJo: ERINA.

88
00:05:44,645 --> 00:05:46,212
SOMETHING WRONG, LOVE?

89
00:05:50,050 --> 00:05:52,218
DEAR, WHAT ARE YOU
CRYING ABOUT?

90
00:05:52,318 --> 00:05:55,388
Erina: THESE TEARS
THAT I'M CRYING ARE FROM JOY,

91
00:05:55,455 --> 00:05:57,791
JOY THAT I AM HERE WITH YOU.

92
00:05:59,125 --> 00:06:03,069
EVEN AS A BOY, YOU STROVE
TO BE A TRUE GENTLEMAN,

93
00:06:03,169 --> 00:06:07,373
A CHAMPION OF OTHERS, NO MATTER
THE CONSEQUENCE TO YOURSELF.

94
00:06:07,407 --> 00:06:10,744
AND NOW THAT PROUD AND NOBLE
JONATHAN JOESTAR

95
00:06:10,811 --> 00:06:12,546
IS HERE IN MY ARMS.

96
00:06:12,579 --> 00:06:14,715
JoJo: AND I HAVE YOU.

97
00:06:14,748 --> 00:06:17,083
WHEN MY HEART
WAS FROZEN IN DESPAIR,

98
00:06:17,150 --> 00:06:20,253
YOU WARMED ME
AND BROUGHT ME BACK TO LIFE.

99
00:06:21,254 --> 00:06:23,857
I AM FORTUNATE
TO HAVE SAVED A WORLD

100
00:06:23,924 --> 00:06:25,391
THAT HAS YOU IN IT.

101
00:06:25,425 --> 00:06:29,095
I ONLY WISH FATHER
COULD HAVE KNOWN YOU.

102
00:06:29,930 --> 00:06:32,933
ERINA, COME. SUPPER IS WAITING.

103
00:06:32,999 --> 00:06:34,768
‐ Erina: JONATHAN!
‐ ( JoJo grunts )

104
00:06:34,868 --> 00:06:36,336
( groaning )

105
00:06:36,402 --> 00:06:38,939
Erina: UM, I WANTED
TO TELL YOU TO BE CAREFUL

106
00:06:39,039 --> 00:06:40,774
SO YOU WOULDN'T BASH YOUR HEAD.

107
00:06:43,777 --> 00:06:45,411
( both laughing )

108
00:06:46,947 --> 00:06:50,517
Erina: AH, I WISH THAT TODAY
WOULD LAST FOREVER.

109
00:06:50,584 --> 00:06:52,519
( wind blowing )

110
00:06:55,455 --> 00:06:58,224
Styx: DAMN, IT FELL
INTO THE ENGINE ROOM.

111
00:06:58,291 --> 00:07:01,267
THAT'S A FILTHY PLACE
TO GO AFTER IT.

112
00:07:01,301 --> 00:07:02,435
( hiccups )

113
00:07:02,468 --> 00:07:03,970
I COULD JUST SELL IT,

114
00:07:04,037 --> 00:07:06,139
BUT IT BRINGS IN THE SHEKELS.

115
00:07:06,239 --> 00:07:07,741
( groans )

116
00:07:07,808 --> 00:07:09,409
DEAR LORD.

117
00:07:09,475 --> 00:07:13,580
YOU SURELY DO SEEM
TO ENJOY PICKING ON ME.

118
00:07:13,647 --> 00:07:15,315
♪

119
00:07:20,486 --> 00:07:21,555
Erina: OH. NO.

120
00:07:21,622 --> 00:07:24,457
I HAVEN'T THE EXPERIENCE
DRINKING A MAN DOES.

121
00:07:24,490 --> 00:07:28,294
JoJo: JUST A BIT,
BARELY ENOUGH TO GET THE TASTE.

122
00:07:28,328 --> 00:07:30,631
IT REALLY ISN'T STRONG AT ALL.

123
00:07:30,664 --> 00:07:32,165
I THINK IT'S GOOD.

124
00:07:34,501 --> 00:07:36,402
HERE.

125
00:07:40,340 --> 00:07:41,608
( chuckles )

126
00:07:41,675 --> 00:07:43,844
( Erina sighs )

127
00:07:43,910 --> 00:07:45,478
JoJo: EH?

128
00:07:45,512 --> 00:07:47,413
( gasps )

129
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:49,650
NO. IT CAN'T BE.

130
00:07:49,683 --> 00:07:51,852
♪

131
00:07:57,023 --> 00:07:58,959
( Erina gasps ) JONATHAN?

132
00:07:59,025 --> 00:08:01,535
( JoJo gasps )
IMPOSSIBLE.

133
00:08:01,602 --> 00:08:02,869
THERE IS NO WAY.

134
00:08:02,969 --> 00:08:05,706
HE'S HERE. DIO'S ALIVE.

135
00:08:05,806 --> 00:08:07,874
( apothecary chuckles )

136
00:08:07,941 --> 00:08:11,144
JoJo: ERINA, GO.
BACK TO OUR CABIN NOW.

137
00:08:11,211 --> 00:08:13,780
AND DON'T FORGET
TO LOCK THE DOOR.

138
00:08:13,847 --> 00:08:15,549
( Erina sighs )

139
00:08:15,649 --> 00:08:17,551
♪

140
00:08:22,789 --> 00:08:24,057
Styx: HUMPH.

141
00:08:24,157 --> 00:08:24,891
EH?

142
00:08:24,991 --> 00:08:27,493
WELL, THAT'S RATHER STRANGE.

143
00:08:27,561 --> 00:08:28,729
THE LOCK'S UNDONE.

144
00:08:28,795 --> 00:08:31,064
QUEER BIT OF BUSINESS.

145
00:08:31,164 --> 00:08:34,901
I CAN SEE A METAL CATCH
GLINTING ON THE INSIDE THERE.

146
00:08:34,968 --> 00:08:36,903
BUT THAT WOULD MEAN...

147
00:08:36,970 --> 00:08:39,640
THAT THIS TRUNK
IS LOCKED FROM THE INSIDE!

148
00:08:41,542 --> 00:08:42,576
( gags )

149
00:08:46,412 --> 00:08:48,081
JoJo: HALT!

150
00:08:48,181 --> 00:08:50,383
YOU CAN'T ESCAPE!

151
00:08:51,585 --> 00:08:53,186
Dio: WHERE IS...

152
00:08:53,253 --> 00:08:54,521
MY BODY?

153
00:08:54,588 --> 00:08:56,590
JoJo: D‐DIO.

154
00:08:56,690 --> 00:08:59,059
Erina: JONATHAN IS SO UPSET.

155
00:08:59,092 --> 00:09:01,401
SOMETHING IS WRONG.

156
00:09:01,434 --> 00:09:03,870
‐ ( zombie growls )
‐ ( woman yelps )

157
00:09:03,937 --> 00:09:05,606
Dio: JOJO.

158
00:09:05,706 --> 00:09:09,342
DO YOU SEE THE CONDITION
IN WHICH I FIND MYSELF?

159
00:09:09,409 --> 00:09:10,611
YOUR WORK.

160
00:09:10,677 --> 00:09:13,947
THERE IS A REASON I
DISPLAY MYSELF TO YOU LIKE THIS.

161
00:09:14,014 --> 00:09:15,248
( JoJo gasps )

162
00:09:15,281 --> 00:09:17,417
Dio: WHY WOULD
I SHOW MY WEAKNESS

163
00:09:17,450 --> 00:09:19,452
TO MY DEADLIEST FOE?

164
00:09:19,553 --> 00:09:22,022
BECAUSE THOUGH
I ONCE DESPISED YOU,

165
00:09:22,088 --> 00:09:25,125
NOW I HAVE ONLY
THE GREATEST RESPECT

166
00:09:25,191 --> 00:09:26,292
FOR YOUR SPIRIT,

167
00:09:26,392 --> 00:09:29,295
YOUR VALOR IN BATTLE,
YOUR POWER.

168
00:09:29,362 --> 00:09:33,299
I SEE IT NOW,
HOW INCREDIBLE YOU ARE.

169
00:09:33,366 --> 00:09:34,467
JoJo: DIO.

170
00:09:34,568 --> 00:09:35,869
Dio: JOJO.

171
00:09:35,936 --> 00:09:38,138
IF NOT FOR YOU,

172
00:09:38,204 --> 00:09:42,242
I WOULD NEVER HAVE OBTAINED
THE POWER OF THE STONE MASK.

173
00:09:42,308 --> 00:09:47,147
HOWEVER, YOUR DAMNABLE MEDDLING
COST ME WORLD DOMINATION.

174
00:09:47,213 --> 00:09:49,082
IF THERE REALLY IS A GOD,

175
00:09:49,149 --> 00:09:51,484
ONE WHO PLUCKS
THE STRINGS OF OUR FATE,

176
00:09:51,585 --> 00:09:55,656
I AM CERTAIN THAT OUR FATES WERE
BOUND TOGETHER FOR A REASON.

177
00:09:57,658 --> 00:10:02,102
OUR TWO EXISTENCES WERE ONLY
EVER INTENDED TO BE BUT ONE,

178
00:10:02,202 --> 00:10:04,370
AND SO I WILL TAKE THE BODY

179
00:10:04,437 --> 00:10:07,107
OF THE ONLY MAN ON EARTH
I RESPECT.

180
00:10:07,173 --> 00:10:09,943
THEN I WILL LIVE
IN ETERNAL GLORY,

181
00:10:10,010 --> 00:10:13,547
FOR THAT IS THE DESTINY
WHICH IS WAITING FOR ME.

182
00:10:13,614 --> 00:10:15,081
THERE WILL BE NO PAIN.

183
00:10:15,115 --> 00:10:18,118
THAT IS THE FINAL GIFT
I BEQUEATH TO YOU.

184
00:10:18,184 --> 00:10:19,620
( JoJo gasps ) NO.

185
00:10:19,686 --> 00:10:21,121
NO, THOSE EYES. I CAN'T...

186
00:10:21,221 --> 00:10:25,425
Dio: LIVE ON AS MY BODY, JOJO!

187
00:10:25,458 --> 00:10:26,893
( JoJo gasps )

188
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,428
Erina: JONATHAN! WHAT‐‐

189
00:10:28,461 --> 00:10:29,863
( JoJo gasps )

190
00:10:29,930 --> 00:10:32,032
ERINA.

191
00:10:39,105 --> 00:10:41,207
( ship's horn blows )

192
00:10:44,477 --> 00:10:45,579
( beams strike )

193
00:10:49,550 --> 00:10:51,451
( JoJo gasps )

194
00:10:52,986 --> 00:10:54,387
( gags )

195
00:10:55,622 --> 00:10:57,791
Erina: NO. JONATHAN.

196
00:10:57,824 --> 00:11:01,334
JoJo: ERI...NA.

197
00:11:01,434 --> 00:11:02,936
Dio: OH...

198
00:11:03,003 --> 00:11:04,638
A PITY YOU WOULDN'T HEAR ME.

199
00:11:04,671 --> 00:11:07,508
IF ONLY YOU HAD REMAINED STILL
AS I TOLD YOU,

200
00:11:07,574 --> 00:11:11,344
YOUR DEATH IN FACT
WOULD HAVE BEEN QUITE PAINLESS.

201
00:11:11,411 --> 00:11:14,247
TORN FROM YOUR
LITTLE FAIRY TALE INTO HELL,

202
00:11:14,314 --> 00:11:17,283
THRUST INTO A REALITY
YOU DIDN'T KNOW EXISTED,

203
00:11:17,350 --> 00:11:20,186
WHAT WILL YOU DO NOW?

204
00:11:20,286 --> 00:11:22,656
DID JOJO NEVER TELL YOU OF ME,

205
00:11:22,689 --> 00:11:26,026
THE EVIL THAT DWELLS THERE
IN THE DARKNESS?

206
00:11:26,092 --> 00:11:28,361
I MAY NOT LOOK
LIKE MUCH RIGHT NOW,

207
00:11:28,428 --> 00:11:32,766
BUT SURELY YOU REMEMBER ME,
ERINA PENDLETON.

208
00:11:32,833 --> 00:11:34,034
WAIT.

209
00:11:34,100 --> 00:11:36,837
IT'S ERINA JOESTAR NOW,
ISN'T IT?

210
00:11:36,870 --> 00:11:37,938
Erina: DIO!

211
00:11:38,004 --> 00:11:38,939
( zombies growling )

212
00:11:39,005 --> 00:11:41,041
( man screams )

213
00:11:41,141 --> 00:11:43,977
THE SHIP'S FULL OF MONSTERS!

214
00:11:44,044 --> 00:11:45,679
‐ ( woman screams )
‐ Man: RUN!

215
00:11:51,718 --> 00:11:53,019
( zombie growling )

216
00:11:53,053 --> 00:11:54,555
( woman gasping )

217
00:11:54,655 --> 00:11:57,157
♪

218
00:12:01,535 --> 00:12:02,836
( Erina gasps )

219
00:12:02,903 --> 00:12:04,738
( baby crying )

220
00:12:04,838 --> 00:12:06,740
( apothecary laughs )

221
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:10,577
AS YOU ORDERED, LORD, I DRAINED
THE LIFE OF ONLY ONE PASSENGER,

222
00:12:10,644 --> 00:12:14,915
AND NOW MOST OF THE SHIP
HAS JOINED OUR LITTLE FAMILY.

223
00:12:15,015 --> 00:12:17,083
( laughs )

224
00:12:17,150 --> 00:12:20,086
AND NOW WE WILL PROCEED
TO AMERICA.

225
00:12:20,186 --> 00:12:21,888
ISN'T THAT RIGHT, LORD DIO?

226
00:12:21,922 --> 00:12:24,257
JoJo: I CAN'T SPEAK.

227
00:12:24,324 --> 00:12:26,827
I CAN'T EVEN TAKE A BREATH.

228
00:12:26,893 --> 00:12:29,095
I HAVE TO MOVE.

229
00:12:29,162 --> 00:12:31,932
ERINA. ERINA.

230
00:12:32,032 --> 00:12:32,933
( gags )

231
00:12:33,033 --> 00:12:35,936
I HAVE TO SAVE‐‐

232
00:12:36,002 --> 00:12:37,270
( yelps )

233
00:12:37,337 --> 00:12:39,172
( apothecary chuckles )

234
00:12:39,239 --> 00:12:40,273
( JoJo gasps )

235
00:12:40,373 --> 00:12:42,943
CAN'T GATHER HAMON.

236
00:12:43,009 --> 00:12:44,444
( apothecary laughs )

237
00:12:44,545 --> 00:12:46,913
WELL, HOW THE MIGHTY
HAVE FALLEN.

238
00:12:46,947 --> 00:12:50,951
THIS SNIVELING WHELP CAN'T
EVEN DRAW A PROPER BREATH NOW.

239
00:12:51,051 --> 00:12:54,521
HE'LL BE CAUSING
NO MORE MISCHIEF WITH HIS HAMON.

240
00:12:54,588 --> 00:12:58,058
THIS IS WHAT HE GETS
FOR CROSSING YOU, LORD DIO.

241
00:12:58,124 --> 00:13:00,460
NOW WE ARE GOING TO PLAY.

242
00:13:00,561 --> 00:13:03,436
OR MAYBE I'LL JUST
SIT QUIETLY AND WATCH

243
00:13:03,469 --> 00:13:06,973
WHILE HE SUFFOCATES SLOWLY.
( chuckles )

244
00:13:07,040 --> 00:13:08,942
Dio: SILENCE, WANG CHEN.

245
00:13:08,975 --> 00:13:11,077
THERE SHALL BE
NO INSULT TO JOJO.

246
00:13:11,144 --> 00:13:13,213
‐ Wang: HUH?
‐ Dio: HE IS THE ONE MAN

247
00:13:13,279 --> 00:13:15,949
CAPABLE OF BRINGING ME
TO THE APEX OF MY FATE.

248
00:13:15,982 --> 00:13:19,485
YOU WILL SHOW HIM ALL
THE RESPECT WHICH IS DUE TO HIM

249
00:13:19,586 --> 00:13:21,955
BY SEVERING HIS HEAD
IN A PAINLESS MANNER.

250
00:13:21,988 --> 00:13:23,757
Wang: OF COURSE, LORD DIO.

251
00:13:23,824 --> 00:13:24,991
( chuckles )

252
00:13:25,058 --> 00:13:29,262
Dio: THE BODY OF MY DEAREST FOE
HAS BECOME MY FUTURE!

253
00:13:29,329 --> 00:13:32,298
‐ Erina: JONATHAN!
‐ ( JoJo gasping )

254
00:13:34,901 --> 00:13:37,137
Dio: HE'S UP TO SOMETHING.

255
00:13:37,170 --> 00:13:38,605
BE CAREFUL.

256
00:13:38,672 --> 00:13:42,175
HE MIGHT HAVE ONE LAST TRICK
UP HIS MUSCLE‐BOUND SLEEVE.

257
00:13:42,242 --> 00:13:44,077
Wang: BAH, HE'S DONE FOR.

258
00:13:44,144 --> 00:13:47,948
LORD DIO OVERESTIMATES
HIS "MIGHTY POWER."

259
00:13:48,014 --> 00:13:49,816
WELL, JONATHAN JOESTAR,

260
00:13:49,850 --> 00:13:52,753
I'LL SCOOP OUT
WHAT LITTLE BRAINS YOU HAVE

261
00:13:52,819 --> 00:13:54,821
WITH MY BARE FINGERS.

262
00:13:54,855 --> 00:13:56,189
JoJo: MUST...

263
00:13:56,256 --> 00:13:57,691
SAVE ERINA.

264
00:13:57,758 --> 00:14:03,537
I HAVE TO USE THE LAST BIT
OF HAMON LEFT IN ME ALL AT ONCE.

265
00:14:03,604 --> 00:14:05,138
PLEASE WORK.

266
00:14:05,205 --> 00:14:06,139
Dio: CAREFUL.

267
00:14:06,206 --> 00:14:07,608
WANG CHEN, LOOK OUT.

268
00:14:07,674 --> 00:14:09,309
( Erina gasps )

269
00:14:12,378 --> 00:14:14,480
‐ ( heart beats )
‐ ( JoJo gasps )

270
00:14:15,481 --> 00:14:19,352
SOMETHING BROKE INSIDE MY BODY,

271
00:14:19,385 --> 00:14:22,055
SOMETHING IMPORTANT.

272
00:14:22,122 --> 00:14:23,056
( Wang sputters )

273
00:14:23,123 --> 00:14:24,558
Dio: WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?

274
00:14:24,658 --> 00:14:26,560
♪

275
00:14:29,896 --> 00:14:32,899
JoJo: TH‐THIS IS THE END,

276
00:14:32,999 --> 00:14:36,169
THE LAST HAMON I HAVE.

277
00:14:36,236 --> 00:14:41,241
TOO WEAK TO DESTROY
THAT ZOMBIE COMPLETELY,

278
00:14:41,307 --> 00:14:43,309
BUT IT WAS ENOUGH.

279
00:14:49,249 --> 00:14:52,553
Dio: WHAT‐‐WHAT IS
HE PLAYING AT?

280
00:14:52,586 --> 00:14:55,355
JOJO HAS INTERFERED
WITH WANG CHEN'S BODY,

281
00:14:55,421 --> 00:14:57,691
DISRUPTING ITS FUNCTIONS

282
00:14:57,758 --> 00:15:00,594
WITHOUT BRINGING IT
TO COMPLETE DESTRUCTION.

283
00:15:00,661 --> 00:15:04,605
HE'S MADE IT SEIZE TIGHTLY
ONTO A PIECE OF MACHINERY,

284
00:15:04,671 --> 00:15:09,009
AND THE DEVICE
IT CLINGS TO SO IMMOVABLY...

285
00:15:09,075 --> 00:15:12,178
IS THE PADDLE'S SCREW SHAFT.

286
00:15:12,245 --> 00:15:14,180
THE STRENGTH OF A ZOMBIE

287
00:15:14,247 --> 00:15:15,949
IS SUFFICIENT
TO ARREST THE PADDLE.

288
00:15:16,049 --> 00:15:17,784
IF THE SHAFT IS STOPPED,

289
00:15:17,851 --> 00:15:21,722
STEAM PRESSURE IN THE PISTON
WILL BUILD UP INEXORABLY.

290
00:15:21,788 --> 00:15:24,958
UNDER SUCH CONDITIONS,
THERE IS BUT ONE END.

291
00:15:25,058 --> 00:15:27,561
THE SHIP WILL EXPLODE!

292
00:15:27,628 --> 00:15:30,631
Erina: JONATHAN,
WHAT'S HAPPENING?

293
00:15:30,697 --> 00:15:33,399
WHY IS THIS HAPPENING TO US?

294
00:15:33,466 --> 00:15:36,737
JoJo: Y‐YOU MUST LEAVE, ERINA.

295
00:15:36,803 --> 00:15:40,807
SOON THE SHIP
WILL BE DESTROYED.

296
00:15:44,911 --> 00:15:47,480
Erina: I DON'T KNOW
HOW THE THINGS

297
00:15:47,581 --> 00:15:49,650
THAT ARE OCCURRING TODAY
ARE POSSIBLE.

298
00:15:49,716 --> 00:15:52,586
IT'S ALL TOO IMPOSSIBLE TO BEAR.

299
00:15:52,653 --> 00:15:55,589
I DON'T KNOW
WHETHER I SHOULD CRY OR SCREAM.

300
00:15:55,656 --> 00:15:59,492
PERHAPS I SHOULD JUST FAINT
DEAD AWAY AND BLOCK IT OUT.

301
00:16:00,493 --> 00:16:04,938
BUT THERE IS ONE THING I KNOW.

302
00:16:05,005 --> 00:16:06,640
ERINA JOESTAR...

303
00:16:08,141 --> 00:16:10,577
WILL REMAIN WITH HER HUSBAND.

304
00:16:10,644 --> 00:16:12,579
♪

305
00:16:14,147 --> 00:16:16,683
IN THE WARMTH OF THESE LIPS,

306
00:16:16,783 --> 00:16:20,954
I FEEL THE COOL EBBING
OF HIS LIFE.

307
00:16:21,021 --> 00:16:24,124
JONATHAN JOESTAR IS DYING,

308
00:16:24,190 --> 00:16:26,426
BUT WE ARE TOGETHER.

309
00:16:26,492 --> 00:16:29,462
I WANT TO STAY LIKE THIS

310
00:16:29,530 --> 00:16:34,434
UNTIL THE SHIP EXPLODES
AND EVERYTHING BURNS TO ASH,

311
00:16:34,500 --> 00:16:37,871
UNTIL EVERYTHING IS GONE.

312
00:16:37,971 --> 00:16:40,674
( machinery creaking )

313
00:16:51,384 --> 00:16:53,520
( baby crying )

314
00:16:55,989 --> 00:16:57,390
( Erina gasps )

315
00:16:57,490 --> 00:17:01,167
JoJo: IT'S ALL RIGHT IF YOU CRY,

316
00:17:01,234 --> 00:17:04,404
BUT YOU HAVE TO...

317
00:17:04,470 --> 00:17:06,406
STAY ALIVE AND GO ON.

318
00:17:06,507 --> 00:17:07,974
( Erina gasps )

319
00:17:08,041 --> 00:17:09,576
JUST LIKE IN A STORYBOOK.

320
00:17:09,676 --> 00:17:13,246
YOU WANT ME TO COME TO THE AID
OF A HELPLESS CHILD

321
00:17:13,346 --> 00:17:14,748
AND ESCAPE TO SAFETY?

322
00:17:14,815 --> 00:17:15,982
( sobs )

323
00:17:16,049 --> 00:17:18,752
THAT'S UNFAIR,
JUST SHEER CRUELTY.

324
00:17:18,819 --> 00:17:23,657
THE ONLY THING THAT I WANT
IS TO END MY LIFE HERE WITH YOU.

325
00:17:24,758 --> 00:17:26,593
JoJo: THAT WOMAN DIED

326
00:17:26,693 --> 00:17:30,531
TRYING TO SAVE HER CHILD
UNTIL THE LAST.

327
00:17:30,597 --> 00:17:34,267
MY OWN MOTHER
DID THE SAME THING FOR ME.

328
00:17:34,367 --> 00:17:36,570
SAVE YOURSELF

329
00:17:36,603 --> 00:17:39,673
TAKE THE BABY. HURRY.

330
00:17:43,109 --> 00:17:46,947
Dio: SO YOUR PLAN IS
TO DESTROY THIS VESSEL, IS IT?

331
00:17:47,047 --> 00:17:49,750
JOJO, YOU NEVER GIVE UP
OR GIVE IN,

332
00:17:49,783 --> 00:17:52,252
NO MATTER THE ODDS,
BUT KNOW THIS.

333
00:17:52,285 --> 00:17:54,588
DETERMINATION
IS NOT JUST IN YOU.

334
00:17:54,621 --> 00:17:58,458
I WILL LIVE.
THERE IS NO ONE WHO CAN DEFY ME!

335
00:17:58,559 --> 00:18:02,035
I WILL TAKE YOUR BODY
AS MY OWN!

336
00:18:02,102 --> 00:18:03,103
ZOMBIES, HITHER!

337
00:18:03,136 --> 00:18:05,305
( zombies growling )

338
00:18:05,405 --> 00:18:07,307
Dio: DEVOUR WANG CHEN'S BODY,

339
00:18:07,373 --> 00:18:09,776
AND RESTART THE PISTON
ONCE YOU HAVE.

340
00:18:14,480 --> 00:18:16,983
JoJo: THE END HAS BEGUN.

341
00:18:17,083 --> 00:18:20,086
‐ ( Dio gasps )
‐ ( steam hissing )

342
00:18:22,756 --> 00:18:24,658
‐ ( Erina gasps )
‐ ( JoJo grunts )

343
00:18:26,560 --> 00:18:27,493
( gags )

344
00:18:27,561 --> 00:18:29,295
( Erina gasps ) JONATHAN.

345
00:18:29,329 --> 00:18:30,897
( JoJo sighs )

346
00:18:30,964 --> 00:18:33,634
( Dio groans )
IT'S ALREADY BLOWING APART.

347
00:18:33,667 --> 00:18:35,435
BUT THERE'S STILL A WAY OUT.

348
00:18:35,502 --> 00:18:39,272
I WAS PROTECTING MYSELF FROM
THE SUN'S RAYS WELL BEFORE THIS.

349
00:18:39,339 --> 00:18:40,774
LET IT EXPLODE.

350
00:18:40,841 --> 00:18:43,677
I ALREADY HAVE
EVERYTHING I NEED TO SURVIVE.

351
00:18:44,678 --> 00:18:45,846
( JoJo gags )

352
00:18:45,946 --> 00:18:47,814
‐ ( baby crying )
‐ ( Erina gasps )

353
00:18:48,682 --> 00:18:50,584
Dio: ERINA, TAKE A GOOD LOOK.

354
00:18:50,651 --> 00:18:53,353
HAH! SINCE JOJO CAN
NO LONGER USE HIS HAMON,

355
00:18:53,419 --> 00:18:57,023
I'LL REMOVE HIS HEAD
AND TAKE HIS BODY AS MY OWN.

356
00:18:57,123 --> 00:19:01,768
THEN I SHALL WALK OVER AND
LIE DOWN IN MY VELVET BOUDOIR.

357
00:19:01,835 --> 00:19:04,971
THAT HUMBLE SHELTER IS
MARVELOUSLY CONSTRUCTED.

358
00:19:05,038 --> 00:19:07,440
IT COULD WITHSTAND
A TON OF DYNAMITE.

359
00:19:07,508 --> 00:19:09,876
GOODBYE, JOJO,

360
00:19:09,943 --> 00:19:14,615
AND WELCOME TO YOU,
MY NEW ETERNAL BODY!

361
00:19:17,117 --> 00:19:19,119
( gags )

362
00:19:19,185 --> 00:19:20,854
Erina: JONATHAN!

363
00:19:20,887 --> 00:19:23,790
( gasps )

364
00:19:27,193 --> 00:19:28,161
JoJo: DIO.

365
00:19:28,228 --> 00:19:29,162
( Dio sputters )

366
00:19:29,229 --> 00:19:30,531
JoJo: AS YOU OBSERVED,

367
00:19:30,564 --> 00:19:34,234
IT MAY BE TRUE THAT OUR FATE
IS TO BE TOGETHER.

368
00:19:34,334 --> 00:19:36,870
I FEEL AN ODD WARMTH FOR YOU,

369
00:19:36,903 --> 00:19:40,741
FOR NOW OUR LIVES ARE
INTERWOVEN COMPLETELY

370
00:19:40,807 --> 00:19:44,545
AND WILL END
ALONG WITH THIS SHIP.

371
00:19:44,578 --> 00:19:46,747
( Erina sobbing )

372
00:19:46,813 --> 00:19:52,085
FAREWELL TO YOU, MY BELOVED.

373
00:19:55,522 --> 00:19:57,190
( Erina gasps, yelps )

374
00:19:57,257 --> 00:20:00,226
Dio: JOJO, LET ME GO!

375
00:20:00,260 --> 00:20:01,034
RELEASE ME.

376
00:20:01,134 --> 00:20:03,269
THINK OF WHAT
WE TWO CAN ACHIEVE.

377
00:20:03,336 --> 00:20:06,039
YOU'D LIKE A TASTE OF ETERNITY,
WOULD YOU NOT?

378
00:20:06,139 --> 00:20:07,808
I CAN HEAL YOUR WOUNDS.

379
00:20:07,874 --> 00:20:11,044
YOU AND ERINA
CAN LIVE TOGETHER FOREVER!

380
00:20:12,345 --> 00:20:13,279
JOJO!

381
00:20:13,346 --> 00:20:15,281
♪

382
00:20:16,550 --> 00:20:19,019
NO. IT'S TOO LATE.

383
00:20:20,386 --> 00:20:22,656
HE'S DEAD.

384
00:20:45,211 --> 00:20:47,748
♪

385
00:20:47,848 --> 00:20:50,350
Erina: JONATHAN JOESTAR
PASSED AWAY

386
00:20:50,416 --> 00:20:54,220
INTO UNDESERVED OBLIVION.

387
00:20:54,254 --> 00:20:57,490
HIS LIFE WAS
AN IMPORTANT PART OF HISTORY,

388
00:20:57,558 --> 00:21:00,333
BUT INVISIBLE
TO ORDINARY PEOPLE.

389
00:21:02,202 --> 00:21:06,206
MOST OF HUMANITY,
FOR WHOM HE SACRIFICED,

390
00:21:06,272 --> 00:21:09,275
WILL NEVER KNOW
OF HIS NOBLE ACCOMPLISHMENTS...

391
00:21:10,544 --> 00:21:12,445
BUT HIS DESCENDANTS WILL.

392
00:21:12,546 --> 00:21:15,248
♪

393
00:21:15,281 --> 00:21:17,918
( baby coos )

394
00:21:19,586 --> 00:21:23,857
Erina: THE LIFE WITHIN ME,
NEWLY CREATED BY JONATHAN AND I,

395
00:21:23,924 --> 00:21:26,727
WILL CERTAINLY HEAR HIS STORY.

396
00:21:31,031 --> 00:21:34,034
Narrator: ERINA JOESTAR
WAS SOON RESCUED

397
00:21:34,100 --> 00:21:36,236
AFLOAT NEAR THE CANARY ISLANDS,

398
00:21:36,302 --> 00:21:41,908
AND THE BOOK OF THE STONE MASK
WAS CLOSED FOR A TIME.

399
00:21:41,975 --> 00:21:48,114
BUT THAT WAS ONLY THE BEGINNING
OF A NEW BIZARRE ADVENTURE.

400
00:21:54,621 --> 00:21:56,757
♪

401
00:22:20,521 --> 00:22:23,690
♪ I'LL BE THE ROUNDABOUT

402
00:22:23,790 --> 00:22:27,528
♪ THE WORDS
WILL MAKE YOU OUT AND OUT ♪

