00:22:54,621 --> 00:22:59,826
♪ I SPEND THE DAY YOUR WAY

409
00:22:59,893 --> 00:23:02,503
♪ CALL IT MORNING
DRIVING THROUGH THE SOUND ♪

410
00:23:02,569 --> 00:23:06,472
♪ AND IN AND OUT THE VALLEY

411
00:23:06,540 --> 00:23:10,043
♪ IN AND AROUND THE LAKE

412
00:23:10,076 --> 00:23:12,412
♪ MOUNTAINS COME
