413
00:23:12,513 --> 00:23:14,748
♪ AND THEY STAND THERE

414
00:23:17,818 --> 00:23:19,385
♪ ONE MILE OVER,
WE'LL BE THERE ♪

415
00:23:19,419 --> 00:23:21,254
♪ AND WE'LL SEE YOU

416
00:23:23,657 --> 00:23:27,861
♪ 10 TRUE SUMMERS, WE'LL BE
THERE AND LAUGHING, TOO ♪

417
00:23:30,363 --> 00:23:32,999
♪ 24 BEFORE, MY LOVE,
YOU'LL SEE ♪

418
00:23:33,066 --> 00:23:37,337
♪ I'LL BE THERE WITH YOU

419
00:23:38,672 --> 00:23:40,607
♪

420
00:23:40,674 --> 00:23:42,375
Man: IT WAS IN THE FALL OF 1938.

421
00:23:42,442 --> 00:23:44,711
Man #2: IT'S GOOD TO SEE YOU
AGAIN, SPEEDWAGON.

422
00:23:44,778 --> 00:23:46,112
Man #3: YOU BASTARD!
HOW COULD YOU

423
00:23:46,179 --> 00:23:47,948
HAVE POSSIBLY
HAVE KNOWN WHERE THEY WERE?

424
00:23:48,014 --> 00:23:49,916
‐ Woman: TEACH HIM A LESSON.
‐ JoJo: JOSEPH JOESTAR.

425
00:23:49,950 --> 00:23:51,785
MY FRIENDS CALL ME JOJO.

